Usage: fix_boundary_overlaps [-help] [-fix_area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]
                             [-groups {string1 string2 ...}]
                             [-hinsts {string1 string2 ...}]
                             [-move_area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-fix_area {x1 y1 x2 y2}           # Specifies the coordinates of the area in
                                  # which overlap needs to be resolved.
                                  # (box, optional)
-groups {string1 string2 ...}     # Specifies the prefixed group names. Use
                                  # this parameter if you want to resolve
                                  # overlaps between only specified groups.
                                  # (list, optional)
-hinsts {string1 string2 ...}     # Specifies the prefixed hinst names. Use
                                  # this parameter if you want to resolve
                                  # overlaps between only specified hinsts.
                                  # (list, optional)
-move_area {x1 y1 x2 y2}          # Specifies the bounding box coordinates.
                                  # (box, optional)